  "body": "How can we fetch data on the server-side with hooks ? I'm working with ```apollojs``` all my calls are inside the ```useEffect``` hook, so they won't be found when I'll call ```getDataFromTree``` on the server [(https://www.apollographql.com/docs/react/features/server-side-rendering.html)](https://www.apollographql.com/docs/react/features/server-side-rendering.html):\r\n\r\n```javascript\r\n  useEffect(() => {\r\n    client\r\n      .query({\r\n        query: gql`\r\n          {\r\n            players {\r\n              name\r\n              image\r\n            }\r\n          }\r\n        `,\r\n      }).then(result => console.log(result));\r\n  }, []);\r\n```",
